description: Alterations to Plot A09 in Phase 1 including a change in residential accommodation mix and alterations to internal layout, basement position and elevations to be treated as a non-material amendment to planning permission 2011/1815 dated 30th March 2012 for demolition of all existing buildings and construction of a mixed use redevelopment to provide residential, commercial, hotel, community and assembly and leisure uses and associated parking, energy centres and new public amenity space.
